05:07.975 --> 05:09.109
- Thrilled to be
on this island.

05:09.242 --> 05:10.478
- Yeah.

05:10.611 --> 05:12.480
- And yes, we'd love
to freshen up.

05:12.613 --> 05:15.015
- Of course. Yeah, Ash will
