05:20.087 --> 05:22.923
- This is Christine Collins,
fresh from Phoenix, Arizona.

05:23.056 --> 05:25.793
- Ms. Collins,
I'm your host Elena Roarke.

05:25.926 --> 05:29.363
- Wonderful to meet you.
Sorry, I'm a bit of a mess.

05:29.497 --> 05:31.499
- It's okay. We'll fix that.

05:35.636 --> 05:37.938
<i>- I'm--I'm-
I'm smelling donuts.</i>

05:38.071 --> 05:40.207
<i>Aah!
* Donut, donut *</i>

05:40.340 --> 05:43.377
- Remixing my epic meltdown
