to look exactly the same.

06:02.630 --> 06:03.997
- I see.

06:04.131 --> 06:06.567
- That's not possible.
I knew it.

06:06.700 --> 06:09.069
- No, no, no.
It's absolutely possible.

06:09.202 --> 06:10.704
But this is Fantasy Island,

06:10.838 --> 06:13.240
and I can make your most
outrageous wish come true.

06:13.373 --> 06:15.843
And that's what you want,
a buffet?

06:15.976 --> 06:19.079
My first job was at this tiny
little station in Amarillo.

06:19.212 --> 06:21.214
I loved it so much.

06:21.348 --> 06:23.250
I was so proud
of my dream job.

06:23.383 --> 06:26.119
One night, I went on a date.

06:26.253 --> 06:28.822
I had a slice of pizza,
had two beers.

06:28.956 --> 06:30.558
We split dessert.

06:30.691 --> 06:36.029
Two days later, I got
my first letter from a viewer.

06:36.163 --> 06:40.434
She was worried
because I had gained weight.

06:40.568 --> 06:42.235
And she was sure that meant

06:42.369 --> 06:45.573
that I was having
some kind of personal problems.

06:45.706 --> 06:47.941
So I have been hungry
ever since.

06:48.075 --> 06:49.877
- I was just wonder...

06:50.010 --> 06:53.947
is it food that you're hungry
for or something deeper?

06:54.081 --> 06:56.416
- I have a therapist. Thanks.

06:56.550 --> 06:58.385
I came here for cheeseburgers.

06:58.519 --> 07:02.089
- Let's get started. Ready?

07:05.192 --> 07:10.864
