- Not one ounce.

07:15.503 --> 07:16.937
You have my word.

07:21.475 --> 07:24.545
- Mmm, mmm.

07:29.216 --> 07:30.751
Mmm!

07:30.884 --> 07:33.420
- Welcome to Fantasy Island.

