pancreatic.

09:14.287 --> 09:16.223
- I'm a goner.

09:16.356 --> 09:17.858
- I'm so sorry.

09:17.991 --> 09:21.228
- Our fantasy is to make her
feel healthy again

09:21.361 --> 09:23.430
just for a few days.

09:23.563 --> 09:27.067
She spent so much of her life
caring for others, for me,

09:27.200 --> 09:29.670
our kids, our grandkids.

09:29.803 --> 09:34.141
I want her to have a weekend
that's all about her.

09:34.274 --> 09:36.710
- And what does
that weekend entail?

09:36.844 --> 09:40.547
- Dancing, walking on
the beach, wonderful food.

09:40.681 --> 09:42.750
- Now, Ruby,
I need to be clear.

09:42.883 --> 09:46.419
Even I can't cure your cancer.
I wish I could.

09:46.553 --> 09:48.221
- I know that, sweetheart.

09:48.355 --> 09:52.292
I'm looking for a fantasy,
not a miracle.

09:53.193 --> 09:56.229
- Most people don't realize
there's a difference.

09:57.097 --> 10:00.634
This map leads you to the place
where the fantasy will begin.

10:02.870 --> 10:05.572
- Thank you for this.
It means the world to us.

10:05.706 --> 10:08.575
- It's my pleasure.

10:08.709 --> 10:11.779
And welcome to Fantasy Island.

10:19.853 --> 10:21.955
- Look out now. Don't want you
to fall and break a hip.

10:22.089 --> 10:24.391
