13:16.129 --> 13:18.932
- It's a date.

13:20.067 --> 13:21.869
- Hey, sweet pea.

13:22.002 --> 13:23.436
- Hmm.

13:23.570 --> 13:26.106
- The gray hair

13:26.239 --> 13:28.876
